          <msContents class="#STM">
            <summary><p>A copy of the <title xml:lang="ta">Nūṟṟeṭṭu Tiruppati Antāti</title>. 114 stanzas: 2 <foreign xml:lang="ta">kāppu</foreign> stanzas + 112 stanzas.</p>

<p>See Zvelebil (1995, p. 76). One of the <title xml:lang="ta">Aṣṭapirapantam</title> by <persName xml:lang="ta" role="author">Piḷḷaip Perumāḷ Aiyaṅkār</persName>, alias <persName xml:lang="ta" role="author">Aḻakiya Maṉavaḷa Tācar</persName>. Possibly by different authors, at least 6 authors and some may be one and the same person. <title xml:lang="ta">Nūṟṟeṭṭu Tiruppati Antāti</title> by <persName xml:lang="ta" role="author">Maṉavaḷa Tācar</persName>.  
  </p>

<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (January 2024).</p>

<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p>    </summary>
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
